      <div class="text">What is better than potatoes and eggs for breakfast? How about served together as a thick omelet served by the slice. This loaf of eggs and potatoes is a dish served all around Spain mainly for breakfast. This dish used to be known as the peasant’s meal due to the dish being very popular around times of famine. </div>
