      <div class="text">This dish is served in many forms but is overall salted cod. You may be able to order it grilled, fried, or stuffed depending on the reteraunt you may be at in Madrid. Restaurants mostly grill the cod, so most likely whatever local restaurant you are in will have grilled Bacalao.</div>
